<PageLayout title="About DJ Misha" description="DJ Misha is a passionate San Diego DJ who has been spinning dance and house music since 2001. Learn about his journey, influences, and professional career.">

  <p>DJ Misha is a dedicated and passionate DJ recognized for his deep love for dance music and his approach to DJing as both an art and a science. He invests significant time in collecting and spinning records, curating sets that introduce audiences to exceptional tracks and unique artists. His intent is to create an environment where people can truly connect with the music, with each performance designed so everyone has an unforgettable time.</p>

  <h2>Professional Career</h2>
  <p>Over the past decade, DJ Misha has become especially popular for weddings, corporate events, and private parties throughout the United States. He often performs alongside live saxophonists, creating a dynamic DJ and sax duo that captivates audiences—a key highlight that has made him a preferred entertainer for major brands such as Salesforce, Intel, and Banana Republic.</p>

  <h2>The Journey</h2>
  <p>DJ Misha's professional journey started with the Southern California rave scene of the late 1990s. Inspired by legendary DJs like Sasha, Digweed, and Paul Oakenfold, he began DJing in 2001, honing his skills in the vibrant San Diego nightlife. He has held residencies at prominent venues in the San Diego Gaslamp Quarter and has shared the stage with acclaimed acts like Kaskade, Mark Farina, and Third Eye Blind.</p>

  <h2>Musical Roots</h2>
  <p>His early life was heavily influenced by a diverse musical upbringing, thanks to his father's vinyl collection. DJ Misha learned both guitar and piano at a young age, and his musical roots encompass everything from disco to classic rock and jazz, including influences like The Beatles and Pink Floyd. This foundation has fueled his ongoing passion for music that now drives his professional DJ career.</p>

  <p>His services today span from intimate gatherings to major festivals, always bringing tailored musical experiences and his signature energy to ensure every event remains lively and memorable.</p>

